{"tid":1864652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"妻為貴州人夫為重慶人　夫婦被卡在邊界兩地都唔畀入","createTime":"2020-02-05T17:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T17:20:05.000Z","uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"090763a106b6922c2d913c520ef3ef73136c05e7","tid":1864652,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZZbWSu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZZbWSu.jpg&h=950eaa1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續，湖北超過10個地方「封城」，浙江溫州亦於昨日（2日）實施人員管控措施，每戶每兩天只可派1人出門。除此之外，內地各處都嚴格限制人們出入，一對夫妻日前就開車從重慶去貴州，由於丈夫是重慶人，妻子是貴州人，結果被卡在兩地交界的橋上，重慶不許貴州人去，貴州不讓重慶人進。<br />\n<br />\n該對夫妻開車從重慶去貴州，開車的丈夫在自己的車上拍攝情況，當他們到貴州的邊界時，邊界人員不讓他開車進去，但稱「貴州媳婦還是可以過來的」、「重慶都不要你了，我們貴州更不得要你進來了」，丈夫不知如何是好，只好放下妻子，自己帶着兒子回頭。<br />\n<br />\n不料到橋的另一頭又被攔截，丈夫解釋「他們也不讓我過去，你們也不准我走，你說哪個辦」。他又指自己本來就在重慶生活，「難道我一直停在這邊，不生活了」。丈夫稱兩邊警察都不讓他進去，因為他老婆是屬於貴州的人重慶不讓她進去，到貴州那邊又不讓四川人的丈夫進去，丈夫無奈地說「真的太難了」，最後只好打電話，看看找不找到熟人幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n影片引來網民的熱論，有人笑稱「小孩放在橋上，男的回重慶，女的回貴州！」、「各回各家，各找各媽！完美解決」，亦有人認為兩邊都不願負責任，「一刀切的辦法，都怕自己的地方惹上瘟疫」、「神奇的國度。一個中國的都不讓進，還怪其他個別國家？」，有網民就指這些高危時期，不應亂跑。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YD4SGj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYD4SGj3.jpg&h=e9cd8e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ORnwWTt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORnwWTt.jpg&h=61539fa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"337dc78478c8dba883bcf1975bb31362e4bb35a0","tid":1864652,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"同胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龍的傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2UmeadN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2UmeadN.jpg&h=9f608806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYSQs0t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYSQs0t.jpg&h=8da5f365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDyHi68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDyHi68.jpg&h=6497431f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcU7vdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcU7vdP.jpg&h=f8a272d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LaB70u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LaB70u.jpg&h=977b8024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abN8Y7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabN8Y7a.jpg&h=7228db99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NtTqNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NtTqNa.jpg&h=d8bd0e3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edea97a804e1a3d5a4e07a930dea324249dd25fc","tid":1864652,"uid":192726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"你不是中國人嗎? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}